Metrics:
1. Setup Prometheus Instance. (done)
2. Prometheus Persistence Solution. 
3. Push Approach: Setup a common jar package to expose metrics to rocket proxy server. (recommended) (1w)
4. Pull Approach: Setup a jar package to start a prometheus embeded web server in java apps. (1w)
5. Grafana Monitoring Dashboard setup. (3d)


